snippet.title: Blaster Master Zero - Official Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Blaster Master Zero from Inti Creates and Sunsoft is coming to the Nintendo Switch on March 9, 2017 in North American and Europe!

Mutant scum never learn! Blaster Master is back!

Official Website: http://blastermaster-zero.com/en/
Twitter (Blaster Master): https://twitter.com/BlasterMasterZ
Twitter (Inti Creates): https://twitter.com/IntiCreatesEN
Facebook (Inti Creates): https://www.facebook.com/inticreates/


Product Details
Title： Blaster Master Zero
Hardware： Nintendo Switch(TM) & Nintendo 3DS 
Genre： Action Adventure
Rating： E for Everyone (Mild Fantasy Violence), PEGI 7
Release Date： March 9th, 2017
Players：TV Mode: 1-2 Players, Tabletop Mode: 1-2 Players, Handheld Mode: 1 Player
Price： $9.99, €9.99, £8.99
Developer： Inti Creates
